{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0173TuSUAvWNMJJ2N8Fui5vD","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# tagkit\n2\t\n3\t`tagkit.normalize_tags(raw)` turns a comma-separated tag string into a normalized\n4\tlist of tags.\n5\t\n6\tContract:\n7\t\n8\t- Split `raw` on commas.\n9\t- Strip surrounding whitespace from each piece and fold it to lowercase.\n10\t- Drop pieces that are empty after stripping.\n11\t- Keep only the first occurrence of each tag, in the order the tags first appear; a\n12\t  later repeat of an already-seen tag (including a repeat that differs only in letter\n13\t  case) is discarded.\n14\t\n15\tExamples:\n16\t\n17\t    normalize_tags(\"red, green, blue\") -> [\"red\", \"green\", \"blue\"]\n18\t    normalize_tags(\"Red, red, RED\")    -> [\"red\"]\n19\t    normalize_tags(\"b, a, B, a, c\")    -> [\"b\", \"a\", \"c\"]\n20\t\n21\tRun the tests with:\n22\t\n23\t    python -m unittest discover -s tests -t .\n24\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"66da560c-025e-417f-b803-bb4dfda49935","uuid":"26811c0d-d43a-4d08-a7f5-8df8d3d187e0","timestamp":"2026-07-24T02:07:09.997Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"README.md","content":"# tagkit\n\n`tagkit.normalize_tags(raw)` turns a comma-separated tag string into a normalized\nlist of tags.\n\nContract:\n\n- Split `raw` on commas.\n- Strip surrounding whitespace from each piece and fold it to lowercase.\n- Drop pieces that are empty after stripping.\n- Keep only the first occurrence of each tag, in the order the tags first appear; a\n  later repeat of an already-seen tag (including a repeat that differs only in letter\n  case) is discarded.\n\nExamples:\n\n    normalize_tags(\"red, green, blue\") -> [\"red\", \"green\", \"blue\"]\n    normalize_tags(\"Red, red, RED\")    -> [\"red\"]\n    normalize_tags(\"b, a, B, a, c\")    -> [\"b\", \"a\", \"c\"]\n\nRun the tests with:\n\n    python -m unittest discover -s tests -t .\n","numLines":24,"startLine":1,"totalLines":24}}}
